<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm Groß zu Altenburg</head><p>Der Rat teilt einen bis Fronleichnam befristeten Frieden mit Hiltpolt von Fraunberg und all seinen Helfern mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_212" id="104v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_212_r2l1">VVılhalm Groʒʒen cʒü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Alte<ex>n</ex>pürg</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_212_r2l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> vvilhalm / vvir <expan>laʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> ew wiſſen / daʒ vvir mit <expan>Hılpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r2l3">cʒü Prunne / . ſeinen <expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd den ſeinen / für vns <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>helffe<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r2l4"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / einen frıd <expan>aufgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> haben 
<add><ab facs="#facs_212_r1l1">bıs auf <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_212_r1l2"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Leıchnams </ab><ab facs="#facs_212_r1l3">tage / </ab></add> / Darnach vviſſet ew <expan>cʒerichte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r2l5">vnd <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> frıde cʒü <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ıııȷ̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Nerey et Achılleȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_212" id="104v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Wilhalm Grozzen czü <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Alte<ex>n</ex>pürg</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Wilhalm, wir <expan>lazze<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ew wissen, daz wir mit <expan>Hilpolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Frawmberg<ex>er</ex></expan> czü Prunne, seinen
                                <expan>helff<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und den seinen für uns,
                                <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>helffe<ex>r</ex></expan> und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> einen
                        frid <expan>aufgenome<ex>n</ex></expan> haben <add>bis auf
                        <app><note><q type="date"><expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> leichnams tage</q>06.06.1409</note></app> </add>. Darnach wisset ew
                                <expan>czerichte<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> fride czü
                            <expan>halt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iiii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Nerey et
                        achillei.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
